<li> is not an early adopter

<li> has never been abducted by aliens or social science researchers

<li> has never received a letter bomb or an anonymous love letter

<li> thinks that ethnic pride is just a better-looking fraternal twin of racism

<li> can do one-handed push-ups

<li> has never parachuted, para-sailed, hang-glided, bungee-jumped, base-jumped,
  surfed, water-skied or played basketball

<li> loves Grand Canyon in July

<li> has written some vile limericks

<li> has come up with some atrocious analogies

