<li> believes that "Underwater Basket-Weaving in the Arctic" is not
  part of Computer Science

<li> eats his apples whole

<li> is ideologically opposed to celery consumption

<li> can subsist on olives, peppers and eggplant

<li> does not possess a high school diploma

<li> says a daily prayer for all vegans 

<li> is a believer in the unmatched healing power of habaneros 

<li> is a strong supporter of animail rights (unless he is hungry) 

<li> has not been arrested to-date

<li> writes unfashionably short recommendation letters

<li> is oblivious of his BMI

